  mid-term → scheme is FROZEN per term once any AssessmentScore exists; weight
  change requires an audited "reset term scores" path (deferred).
- SECURITY DEFINER count stays 4; seeding rides the existing signup tx
  (NOT withTenant), same as Phase 1 ClassLevel seed.

